Fix: Reformat Bitlocker Enabled Acer TravelMate P

Quick Steps:
1. USB: Make Windows 11 bootable USB.
2. BIOS: Boot → F2/F12.
3. VMD Controller: Main tab → Ctrl + S → Disable.
4. Boot Order: Boot tab → USB first → Save & Exit.
5. Disk Clean:
   diskpart
   list disk
   select disk 0
   clean
   exit

6. Install Windows: Fresh install → Reinstall drivers via Windows Update / Acer Support.
